# JARVIS – AI Desktop Voice Assistant

A dynamic desktop voice assistant inspired by the fictional AI assistant J.A.R.V.I.S..
This project provides a local AI-powered assistant capable of voice interaction, command automation, and a graphical interface.

The assistant uses offline speech recognition with OpenAI Whisper and a GUI built with Kivy.

---

# Features

* Wake word activation (**"Jarvis"**)
* Automatic speech recognition
* Whisper fallback recognition
* Automatic language detection
* Dynamic command interpretation
* Multi-command execution
* Keyboard command fallback
* GUI interface
* Desktop automation
* Conversation memory

Example commands:

```
Jarvis open youtube
Jarvis open chrome and search python tutorial
Jarvis play ai news
Jarvis what time is it
Jarvis shutdown computer
```

If voice recognition fails after 3 attempts, Jarvis automatically switches to **text command mode**.

